\">+25.3%</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;color:#64748b;font-size:12px;\">Neuromodulation. No CAPR read-through.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;font-size:13px;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;\">\n      <th style=\"padding:5px 8px;text-align:left;color:#dc2626;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;\">Top Losers</th>\n      <th style=\"padding:5px 8px;text-align:right;color:#94a3b8;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;\">Move</th>\n      <th style=\"padding:5px 8px;text-align:left;color:#94a3b8;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;\">Read-through</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;\">POM</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626;\">&#8722;27.9%</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;color:#64748b;font-size:12px;\">Not in portfolio. No CAPR read-through.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;font-weight:700;color:#1e293b;\">DARE</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#dc2626;\">&#8722;27.1%</td>\n      <td style=\"padding:6px 8px;color:#64748b;font-size:12px;\">Not in portfolio. No CAPR read-through.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-top:10px;padding:8px 12px;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;\">\n    &#128161; ZYBT +322% confirms the exact payoff pattern you're targeting for CAPR. These moves happen. The setup requires patience in the days before &#8212; you're 8 days out.\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- LARGE-CAP EARNINGS ON DECK -->\n<div style=\"padding:16px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;\">LARGE-CAP EARNINGS ON DECK</div>\n\n  <table style=\"bord